SBG: select TOP 1 MeasureValue from DC_CV_IMSGW_SBG_RAW where UTC_DATETIME_ID=@time and NODE_NAME=@node and MEASURED_OBJECT = @measuredObject and MEASURE_ID in (SELECT MEASURE_ID FROM DIM_CV_MEASURE where MEASURE_NAME=@name ) order by MeasureValue
MTAS: select TOP 1 MeasureValue from DC_CV_MTAS_MTAS_RAW where UTC_DATETIME_ID=@time and ROWSTATUS='LOADED' and NODE_NAME=@node and MEASURED_OBJECT = @measuredObject and MEASURE_ID in (SELECT MEASURE_ID FROM DIM_CV_MEASURE where MEASURE_NAME=@name ) order by MeasureValue
GGSN: select TOP 1 MeasureValue from DC_CV_GGSN_PGW_RAW where UTC_DATETIME_ID=@time and ROWSTATUS='LOADED' and NODE_NAME=@node and MEASURED_OBJECT = @measuredObject and MEASURE_ID in (SELECT MEASURE_ID FROM DIM_CV_MEASURE where MEASURE_NAME=@name ) order by MeasureValue
ERBS_V_RAW: select TOP 1 MeasureValue from DC_CV_ERBS_EUTRANCELL_V_RAW where UTC_DATETIME_ID=@time AND NODE_NAME=@node AND DCVECTOR_INDEX=1 and CELL_FDN=@cell_fdn and MEASURE_ID in (SELECT MEASURE_ID FROM DIM_CV_MEASURE where MEASURE_NAME=@name ) order by MeasureValue
